{"article_id":"z5Nyjo3zEPZ7orO1","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Over the months , Hillary Clinton misstated key facts about her use of private email and her own server for her work as secretary of state ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"the department 's inspector general reported this week .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"According to the findings ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"she claimed approval","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"she did n't have","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"and declined to be interviewed for the report","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"despite saying :","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"`` I 'm more than ready to talk to anybody anytime . ''","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"Scrutiny of her unusual email practices appeared to be unwelcome ,","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"despite her contention","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"those practices were well known and `` fully above board . ''","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"A look at some of Clinton 's past claims about her unusual email set-up and how they compare with the inspector general 's findings :","depth":4},{"id":12,"text":"CLINTON :","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"`` The system","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"we used","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"was set up for President Clinton 's office .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"And it had numerous safeguards .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"It was on property","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"guarded by the Secret Service .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"And there were no security breaches . ''","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"- March 2015 press conference .","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"THE REPORT :","depth":4},{"id":22,"text":"Evidence emerged of hacking attempts ,","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"though it 's unclear whether they were successful .","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"On Jan. 9 , 2011 ,","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"( asterisk )","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"an adviser to former President Bill Clinton notified the State Department 's deputy chief of staff for operations","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"that he had to shut down the server","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"because he suspected","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"`` someone was trying to hack us","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"and","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"while they did not get in","depth":14},{"id":32,"text":"i did. , nt","depth":15},{"id":33,"text":"( sic ) want to let them have the chance to . ''","depth":15},{"id":34,"text":"Later that day , he sent another note .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"`` We were attacked again","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"so I shut","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"( the server )","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"down for a few min . ''","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"The following day the deputy chief emailed top Clinton aides","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"and instructed them not to email the secretary `` anything sensitive . ''","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"Also in May 2011 , Clinton told aides","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"that someone was `` hacking into her email , ''","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"after she received a message with a suspicious link ,","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"the new audit report said .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"The Associated Press has previously reported","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"that ,","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"according to detailed records","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"compiled in 2012 ,","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"Clinton 's server was connected to the internet in ways","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"that made it more vulnerable to hackers .","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"It appeared to allow users to connect openly over the internet","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"to control it remotely .","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"Moreover , it 's unclear what protection her email system might have achieved","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"from having the Secret Service guard the property .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"Digital security breaches tend to come from computer networks , not over a fence .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"CLINTON :","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"`` What I did was allowed .","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"It was allowed by the State Department .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"The State Department has confirmed that . ''","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"- AP interview , September .","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"THE REPORT :","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"`` No evidence ''","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"that Clinton asked for or received approval","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"to conduct official government business on a personal email account","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"run through a private server in her New York home .","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"According to top State Department officials","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"interviewed for the investigation ,","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"the departments","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"that oversee security","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"`` did not","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"- and would not -","depth":14},{"id":72,"text":"approve '' her use of a personal account","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"because of security concerns .","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"Clinton has changed her account","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"since the report came out .","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"On Thursday , she told CNN","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"`` I thought","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"it was allowed .","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"I knew","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"past secretaries of state used personal email . ''","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"Colin Powell was the only secretary of state","depth":14},{"id":82,"text":"who used personal email for work ,","depth":15},{"id":83,"text":"but not to the extent","depth":16},{"id":84,"text":"she did ,","depth":16},{"id":85,"text":"and he did not use a private server .","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"CLINTON :","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"`` It was fully above board .","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"Everybody in the government","depth":16},{"id":89,"text":"with whom I emailed","depth":16},{"id":90,"text":"knew","depth":15},{"id":91,"text":"that I was using a personal email . ''","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"- AP interview , September .","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"CLINTON :","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"`` The people in the government knew","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"that I was using a personal account .","depth":14},{"id":96,"text":"the people","depth":16},{"id":97,"text":"I was emailing to on the dot gov system","depth":16},{"id":98,"text":"certainly knew","depth":15},{"id":99,"text":"and they would respond to me on my personal email . ''","depth":14},{"id":100,"text":"- NBC News interview , September .","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"THE REPORT :","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"According to the findings ,","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"it 's unclear how widespread knowledge was about Clinton 's use of a personal account .","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"Though Clinton 's use of a private email was discussed with some in her agency ,","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"senior department officials","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"who worked for her ,","depth":14},{"id":107,"text":"including the undersecretary","depth":15},{"id":108,"text":"responsible for security ,","depth":15},{"id":109,"text":"said","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"they were not asked to approve or review the use of her private server .","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"The officials also said","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"they were `` unaware of the scope or extent '' of her email practices ,","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"even though Clinton exchanged hundreds of thousands of messages with people in government from her personal account .","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"CLINTON :","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"`` In the fall ,","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"I think","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"it was October of last year","depth":14},{"id":118,"text":"( 2014 ) ,","depth":14},{"id":119,"text":"the State Department sent a letter to previous secretaries of state","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"asking for help with their record-keeping ,","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"in part because of the technical problems","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"that they knew","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"they had to deal with .","depth":14},{"id":124,"text":"And they asked","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"that we , all of us , go through our e-mails","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"to determine what was work-related","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"and to provide that for them . ''","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"- NBC News , September .","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"THE REPORT :","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"While it 's true that the State Department requested records from former secretaries of state in November 2014 ,","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"the report says","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"the department raised concerns about Clinton 's compliance with federal record-keeping laws years earlier ,","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"and the attention did not appear welcome .","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"Two employees in the Office of Information Resources Management discussed concerns about her use of a personal email account in separate 2010 meetings .","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"One of the employees stressed in one of the meetings","depth":13},{"id":136,"text":"that the information","depth":16},{"id":137,"text":"being transmitted","depth":16},{"id":138,"text":"needed to be preserved","depth":15},{"id":139,"text":"to satisfy federal records laws .","depth":14},{"id":140,"text":"They were instructed by the director of the department `` never to speak of the Secretary 's personal email system again , ''","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"according to the report .","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"CLINTON :","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"`` I think","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"last August","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"I made it clear","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"I 'm more than ready to talk to anybody anytime .","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"- CBS News interview in May .","depth":8},{"id":148,"text":"THE REPORT :","depth":7},{"id":149,"text":"Clinton declined through her lawyer","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"to be interviewed for the report .","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"Four other secretaries of state participated :","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"John Kerry , Madeleine Albright , Condoleezza Rice and Colin Powell .","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"She now says :","depth":10},{"id":154,"text":"`` everything","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"I had to say","depth":12},{"id":156,"text":"was out there . ''","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"But she has said","depth":10},{"id":158,"text":"she will speak to the FBI as part of a separate criminal investigation into possible security breaches","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"related to her private server .","depth":11},{"id":160,"text":"In October , she testified about the issue before the House committee","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"investigating the 2012 Benghazi attacks .","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"Get the Monitor Stories","depth":4},{"id":163,"text":"you care about","depth":4},{"id":164,"text":"delivered to your inbox .","depth":3},{"id":165,"text":"By signing up ,","depth":3},{"id":166,"text":"you agree to our Privacy Policy","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":333,"left":328,"right":332,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":328,"left":187,"right":327,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":187,"left":177,"right":186,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":177,"left":168,"right":176,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":168,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":176,"left":173,"right":175,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":173,"left":2,"right":172,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":172,"left":169,"right":171,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":169,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":171,"left":5,"right":170,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":170,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nucl